metadata.name: Private Paradise (the first puzzle)
metadata.description: What gives the carpet an imaginary identity is an idea that was originally the basis for its design. The carpet is a small paradise, once promised to be a better place to live. To bring peace into the home. To spread imagination on the floor of the house. The carpet is a mirror of heaven in the vision of a person who believed that there is hope to live one day in eternal peace. An idea that nowadays is very far away...Very far away...
